{"word":"G591 - ἀποδίδωμι - apodídōmi - ap-od-eed'-o-mee - Deliver","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀποδίδωμι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apodídōmi</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-od-eed'-o-mee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Deliver</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கொடுத்து தீர், பலனளி, கடனைத் தீர், செலுத்து, ஒப்புக்கொடு, பதிலளி, கொடு"},{"paragraph":"to put away by giving, to give up, give over, to deliver, to pay off, discharge"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and <a href=\"#/G1325 - δίδωμι - dídōmi - did'-o-mee/1325\">G1325</a>; to <i>give away</i>, that is, <i>up</i>, <i>over</i>, <i>back</i>, etc. (in various applications): - deliver (again), give (again), (re-) pay (-ment be made), perform, recompense, render, requite, restore, reward, sell, yield,</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1325/1325\">G1325</a>, <a href=\"#/G1431/1431\">G1431</a>, <a href=\"#/G1432/1432\">G1432</a>, <a href=\"#/G1433/1433\">G1433</a>, <a href=\"#/G1434/1434\">G1434</a>, <a href=\"#/G1435/1435\">G1435</a>, <a href=\"#/G3860/3860\">G3860</a>, <a href=\"#/G3862/3862\">G3862</a>, <a href=\"#/G467/467\">G467</a>, <a href=\"#/G468/468\">G468</a>, <a href=\"#/G469/469\">G469</a>, <a href=\"#/G591/591\">G591</a>"}]}